# Smart Coupled Flow–Geomechanical Upscaling for Oil Sands

This repository contains the source code and scripts used in the MSc thesis:

Ou, X. (2026). Smart Coupled Flow–Geomechanical Upscaling Technique for Oil Sands.

University of Alberta.

## Contents

- 3DCNN model for predicting soil response
- Data preprocessing scripts
- Upscaling procedures for anisotropic parameters
- FLAC3D implementation of anisotropic strain-softening model

## Requirements

Python 3.10  
PyTorch  
NumPy  
FLAC3D 7.0

## Project Status

This repository contains code developed as part of an MSc thesis at the University of Alberta.

The associated research is currently being prepared for journal publication. The repository is shared to support transparency and reproducibility of the thesis.

The methodology and results may be further refined in future publications.
